description: Welcome to the exceptional penthouse unit at 324 W 4th Street. Elegance and charm define the Savannah Condominium Residences, a 100% owner-occupied building in the heart of South Boston, deriving its name from the southern-styled design. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by high ceilings that create an open, airy atmosphere throughout the penthouse. Natural light floods the interior, emphasizing the spaciousness of the open-concept layout & lending a warm, inviting ambiance. The first floor features two bedrooms & two en suite bathrooms with luxurious heated floors. The top floor houses a loft, ideal for guests or working from home. Step outside and discover the true beauty of this residence with THREE outdoor spaces. The crowning jewel is the expansive roof deck with direct gas lines ready for your grill and fire pit. On-site parking ensures the convenience desired in city living. Building complete w/ gym + private storage. Beyond your doorstep lies the vibrant neighborhood of Southie.
